name: Whereabouts Unknown 003
description: "In our restlessness we're always tempted to climb every hill to see what lies beyond. But if you must follow that trail up the mountainside to its bitter end, you will discover that it leads eventually right back to the suburbs. But the truth is that it goes to every single place that it crosses. It leads also to where you are standing and watching it. You are already in the true beyond to which is leads."
